Layout basics:
  linear — flex-direction column/row. children stack along the axis. Use expanded/flexible children for proportional sizing.
  box — CSS box model: width, height, padding, margin, decoration (color, borderRadius, border, boxShadow). child = single child.
  stack — overlay children. Use positioned children for absolute placement within the stack.
  padding / margin — shorthand wrappers. Accept string M3 token ("sm", "md", "lg", etc.) or EdgeInsets object {all}, {horizontal,vertical}, {top,right,bottom,left}.

Action types (type field):
  tool — call an MCP tool. {"type": "tool", "tool": "save", "params": {"id": "{{item.id}}"}}
  state — mutate state. {"type": "state", "action": "set", "binding": "filter", "value": "active"}
  navigation — route change. {"type": "navigation", "action": "push", "route": "/detail"}
  batch — run multiple actions. {"type": "batch", "actions": [...]}
  notification — show snackbar/toast. {"type": "notification", "message": "Saved", "severity": "success"}
  openApp / exitApp (v1.3) — dashboard-to-full-app transition / close signal.

Tool action auto-merge: on success, top-level keys of the tool's JSON response are merged into page state automatically. Suppress with bindResult field.

Lifecycle hooks: onInit (app) / onReady (page) / onDestroy run actions at the corresponding lifecycle point.

Reference: specs/mcp_ui_dsl/spec/1.3/04_Actions.md, 02_Widgets.md §2.4
